{"tid":1813880,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"TWICE MOMO首談男朋友　4頁手寫信公開","createTime":"2020-01-06T14:51:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-07T05:49:02.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"81641f1b6df45900d52ea6a690396745d2166083","tid":1813880,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T14:51:53.000Z","msg":"南韓女團TWICE成員MOMO新的一年認愛SJ希澈，今（6日）手寫信回應戀情跟粉絲致歉，因為2020一開始就因為戀愛嚇到各位，雖然會帶來傷害，但還是想親自與大家對話與溝通。<br />\n<br />\nMOMO手寫4張信於官方後援會公開，首度談起與希澈的戀情，表示每年都跟粉絲留下美好回憶，結果2020第一天就傳出戀愛傳聞嚇到ONCE（粉絲名）感到抱歉，但因為「ONCE是支撐TWICE的力量」，苦惱許久仍決定要與大家溝通與對話，喊話即使生活上的事情讓各位不開心，她們還是會小心翼翼，希望成員與粉絲都能健健康康。<br />\n<br />\nSana與娜璉也發文，表示她們也是人，會受傷、會犯錯、會讓人感到失望，但TWICE還是想成為粉絲的力量，感謝今年因為大家，讓她們得到很多獎項，若各位覺得心煩不想做任何事，就關掉手機電源休息，別被瑣碎的事影響心情與生活。<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.nownews.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/1578296040-e446774a44d67f834b7deb1912848e6a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nownews.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F01%2F1578296040-e446774a44d67f834b7deb1912848e6a.jpg&h=9f7b6d3b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3d1b83b07c7e6ab5b1258966ffb88eac8abd904a","tid":1813880,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T14:52:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://66.media.tumblr.com/b08b49ec9923fe4327a9a125acfc1bec/8d40df166c7a7076-6d/s400x600/ac9294f1d2de4e07328502cc064bbc0cc3fdf1c3.gifv\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F66.media.tumblr.com%2Fb08b49ec9923fe4327a9a125acfc1bec%2F8d40df166c7a7076-6d%2Fs400x600%2Fac9294f1d2de4e07328502cc064bbc0cc3fdf1c3.gifv&h=345c9c39&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://66.media.tumblr.com/3f3d3dd8cdf4eff8d5cabd061a5cf71f/8d40df166c7a7076-b4/s400x600/209a95c762d60008aa67c1ceec2306d9145c58aa.gifv\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F66.media.tumblr.com%2F3f3d3dd8cdf4eff8d5cabd061a5cf71f%2F8d40df166c7a7076-b4%2Fs400x600%2F209a95c762d60008aa67c1ceec2306d9145c58aa.gifv&h=8c3ec2a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n原諒牙毛未<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a993c97333032db1fef9f4a959125bc8765d3688","tid":1813880,"uid":205928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T14:56:18.000Z","msg":"有冇翻譯=="},{"pid":"18e83ae5857fe989a908e95d5e45b4e60dd499fa","tid":1813880,"uid":37146,"like":12,"dislike":3,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T14:56:35.000Z","msg":"代表ONCE表示不原諒，退團啦仆街"},{"pid":"3c5759e48b6a970c1a70f6204a3e035b3a19d7b3","tid":1813880,"uid":87394,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T14:58:54.000Z","msg":"本身都諗住原諒<br />\n但隊長咁臭串不了"},{"pid":"15e925eee7c6198e4d9a33ef321b29c792406ba2","tid":1813880,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T15:00:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://66.media.tumblr.com/eb5f83f5fcdff8c87e5cf75efe393c55/5f17239926e48cfb-53/s500x750/cd5485fdc5f451b5213fda69602b15bc01b09b2d.gifv\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F66.media.tumblr.com%2Feb5f83f5fcdff8c87e5cf75efe393c55%2F5f17239926e48cfb-53%2Fs500x750%2Fcd5485fdc5f451b5213fda69602b15bc01b09b2d.gifv&h=6bd4daa1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://66.media.tumblr.com/5b67a01d8f9679bb3fa777f6f3d4454e/5f17239926e48cfb-f1/s500x750/1772ee5c9914a39dfed48b6374d9e4d3aced378c.gifv\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F66.media.tumblr.com%2F5b67a01d8f9679bb3fa777f6f3d4454e%2F5f17239926e48cfb-f1%2Fs500x750%2F1772ee5c9914a39dfed48b6374d9e4d3aced378c.gifv&h=1d0ed23b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://66.media.tumblr.com/cc846c014993e6debd9a61d15871726c/5f17239926e48cfb-fd/s500x750/ab0ec1cbf29189f963148b3413f6ccd784f45178.gifv\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F66.media.tumblr.com%2Fcc846c014993e6debd9a61d15871726c%2F5f17239926e48cfb-fd%2Fs500x750%2Fab0ec1cbf29189f963148b3413f6ccd784f45178.gifv&h=5f4c7869&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://66.media.tumblr.com/9371c03dd181dc4323884b35d